******************************************************
Authentication readMe

A virtual environment is required for the Django website to function

pip install virtualenv
virtualenv venv                  #naming the environment venv
source venv/bin/activate         #to activate the virtual environment

pip install Django               #make sure Django is installed
cd authentication
python manage.py makemigrations  #updates and creates tables as needed
python manage.py migrate         #synchronize model changes with the database scheme
python manage.py runserver       #activates the server

into a browser, type " http://127.0.0.1:8000/ " to verify if it works
into a browser, type " http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin " to see the actual login page

